Package: NegBinomHMC
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Negative Binomial Regression via Hamiltonian Monte Carlo
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Weixiong Hua", "Yi Liu",
      email = "wxhua@umich.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for simulating and fitting Negative Binomial regression
    models using Hamiltonian Monte Carlo (HMC). Includes functionality for
    log-posterior and gradient computation, step-size adaptation, and posterior
    sampling for overdispersed count data. Useful for Bayesian modeling of
    count outcomes where Poisson models are insufficient.
